            "favourites_count": 1,
            "edited_at": null,
            "content": "<p>When you have been community activists as long as we have, you realize that many of the problems we are trying to resolve at the local level are reinforced and buttressed by some very broad and ubiquitous underlying assumptions.</p><p>Assumptions about human exceptionalism, infinite growth and a denial of inter-generational accountability.<br> <br>While we continue to work on many local issues, we also feel it is important to poke holes in those assumptions by starting conversations about how humanity might thrive for the long term.</p><p>The effects of doing this will not be felt in the short term, but over time, many seemingly intractable problems will become much easier to resolve.</p><p><a href=\"http://www.aspenproposal.org\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" translate=\"no\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://www.</span><span class=\"\">aspenproposal.org</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a></p><p><a href=\"https://universeodon.com/tags/sustainability\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>sustainability</span></a> <a href=\"https://universeodon.com/tags/spirituality\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>spirituality</span></a> <a href=\"https://universeodon.com/tags/ClimateChange\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>ClimateChange</span></a> <a href=\"https://universeodon.com/tags/biodiversity\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>biodiversity</span></a> <a href=\"https://universeodon.com/tags/nature\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>nature</span></a> <a href=\"https://universeodon.com/tags/politics\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>politics</span></a> <a href=\"https://universeodon.com/tags/economics\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>economics</span></a> <a href=\"https://universeodon.com/tags/environment\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>environment</span></a></p>",
            "reblog": null,
