                "note": "<p>\"Aspen\" is an acronym for \"Attempting to See Past the Ends of our Noses\".  A small group of folks in the mountains of British Columbia have written a brief description of the necessary elements of a sustainable civilization. We are using it to promote conversations and thought about the long-term, in order to accelerate a paradigm shift.</p>",
